Package org.cytoscape.model.events

Class SetNetworkPointerEvent

java.lang.Object
org.cytoscape.event.AbstractCyEvent<CyNode>
org.cytoscape.model.events.SetNetworkPointerEvent
All Implemented Interfaces:
CyEvent<CyNode>
public final class SetNetworkPointerEvent extends AbstractCyEvent<CyNode>
Used to track setting of nested networks on nodes.

Cytoscape Backwards Compatibility (Final Class): This class is final and therefore can't be extended by users. This means that we may add methods for minor version updates. Methods will only be removed for major version updates.

Module: model-api

To use this in your app, include the following dependency in your POM:

<dependency>
    <groupId>org.cytoscape</groupId>
    <artifactId>model-api</artifactId>
</dependency>
